      <title>特朗普宣誓就职的亿万富翁从那以后损失了2009亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/billionaires-at-trump-s-swearing-in-have-since-lost-200-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）于1月20日宣誓就职时，他被一些世界上最富有的人所围着。当天在场的亿万富翁;包括Elon Musk，Jeff Bezos和Mark Zuckerberg＆Mdash;从来没有富有富裕，充满了泡沫股市的巨大收益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/billionaires-at-trump-s-swearing-in-have-since-lost-200-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 19:15:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
